article_id:1204,category_name:Updates,title_name:Version Update [Update],image_path:,message:<div>Update 1.18.2, which fixes certain issues, will be available for download around <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1585623600"></span>.</div><div>You may install it when it becomes available; otherwise, an automatic update will occur at approximately <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1585710000"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>■Notes:</div><div>It may take time for the store to reflect the updated information. Players may not be able to perform updates due to their device&#39;s data cache being full. If you are unable to perform the update, restart your device, and then try downloading it from the store.</div><div><br></div><div><span style="color: rgb(41, 105, 176);"><strong>[Addendum <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1585710000"></span>]</strong></span></div><div>As a token of our appreciation, the following item has been sent to players who started playing before <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1585710000"></span>.</div><div><br>・Tenfold Summon Voucher x1</div><div><br>This gift can be claimed from your goodie box for up to seven days after reception. If the gift isn&#39;t retrieved within seven days, it will be lost.</div><div><br>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1585623600,update_time1585710079